525
00:35:14,335 --> 00:35:19,757
"Yeah, that's it. Enjoy your four-hour
ride home on that stinking bus."

526
00:35:21,509 --> 00:35:26,931
So I said to Nick, "Do you have any
other versions of 'stinking bus'?"

527
00:35:27,015 --> 00:35:29,183
Nick, what did you say?

528
00:35:29,267 --> 00:35:31,561
I said I got 57 takes.

529
00:35:31,644 --> 00:35:36,774
Which he really did, 'cause we
worked it to death there in New York.

530
00:35:38,067 --> 00:35:42,405
He said, "I have..." It wasn't 57.
The actual number was...

531
00:35:42,488 --> 00:35:46,367
- It was like 36 takes.
- "I have 36 takes of 'stinking bus."'

532
00:35:46,451 --> 00:35:50,079
I go, "That's the title
of your autobiography."

533
00:35:50,163 --> 00:35:52,957
- Thirty-six Takes...
- 36 Takes of Stinking Bus:

534
00:35:53,041 --> 00:35:56,419
- Nick Fletcher Story.
