535
00:35:56,502 --> 00:36:00,840
It's They Call Me Ma'am. Steve cuts
his hair in a very distinctive fashion.

536
00:36:00,924 --> 00:36:05,929
We've never been able to figure out how
Steve gets professional hair cutters

537
00:36:06,012 --> 00:36:07,764
to do this to his hair.

538
00:36:07,847 --> 00:36:12,477
But anyway, throughout his life,
waiters and various...

539
00:36:12,560 --> 00:36:14,979
- Police officers.
...servant people...

540
00:36:15,063 --> 00:36:19,067
- Stewardesses.
