935
01:02:19,210 --> 01:02:24,632
And itjust hit me like...
This went to...

936
01:02:24,716 --> 01:02:28,428
In a good screenplay,
it's get that character up a tree,

937
01:02:28,511 --> 01:02:31,222
- then you got to get him down.
- Right.

938
01:02:32,265 --> 01:02:38,062
This sequence is the best it's been
because we had it like a smorgasbord

939
01:02:38,146 --> 01:02:40,481
