01:05:09,297 --> 01:05:13,426
Remember when the sword was missing
in some scenes?

981
01:05:13,509 --> 01:05:16,429
- Yes, he did know.
- I didn't realise it,

982
01:05:16,512 --> 01:05:20,892
and then I was upset we were putting it
