1003
01:06:25,623 --> 01:06:28,418
- And silver.
- Any colour you want to be high-tech

1004
01:06:28,501 --> 01:06:31,004
- is high-tech.
- The great thing about this

1005
01:06:31,087 --> 01:06:34,257
is it's very moving,
but we also got in two greatjokes.

1006
01:06:34,340 --> 01:06:35,967
Yeah.

1007
01:06:37,802 --> 01:06:42,265
- Renée, I love in this scene.
