1010
01:06:51,232 --> 01:06:55,194
This thing with the suicide pact,

1011
01:06:55,278 --> 01:06:59,324
and this was Morgan...
What's his last name?

1012
01:06:59,407 --> 01:07:00,825
- Kelly.
- Morgan Kelly.

1013
01:07:00,909 --> 01:07:03,703
One of my favourite laughs.
