1014
01:07:03,786 --> 01:07:09,000
off of something this small.
When she says, "That kills you twice",

1015
01:07:09,083 --> 01:07:11,711
and he does that little thing
on his lip.

1016
01:07:11,794 --> 01:07:15,965
The reason you laugh
is the acting is so good.

1017
01:07:16,049 --> 01:07:18,801
The way people would say "right".

1018
01:07:18,885 --> 01:07:22,222
Does any bee wear
a short-sleeve shirt with buttons?

1019
01:07:22,305 --> 01:07:24,599
- All sweaters?
- They wear polo shirts.

1020
01:07:24,682 --> 01:07:28,019
- Polo shirts.
- I love that two-shot as well.

1021
01:07:28,102 --> 01:07:30,313
- I do too.
- If you think about that,

1022
01:07:30,396 --> 01:07:34,609
of where would you put the camera
to get the bee and the girl in the shot,

1023
01:07:34,692 --> 01:07:39,530
- it's great.
- This is a scene that we boarded

1024
01:07:39,614 --> 01:07:42,533
and it really never changed
in three years.

1025
01:07:55,380 --> 01:08:00,551
That line there, "I had to open my mouth
and talk", that's the most sincere

1026
01:08:00,635 --> 01:08:03,763
I've ever done anything
in the show business industry.

1027
01:08:03,846 --> 01:08:06,558
- I actually had to be sincere.
- Was that hard?

1028
01:08:06,641 --> 01:08:10,019
- So hard and uncomfortable.
- It was hard to get it out of you.

1029
01:08:10,103 --> 01:08:13,273
- I just hated it.
- So you were never sincere?

1030
01:08:13,356 --> 01:08:17,277
Yeah, it works, but it was excruciating.
Like a needle at the doctor.

1031
01:08:17,360 --> 01:08:21,155
- That bad to be sincere?
- You said, "You need to be sincere

1032
01:08:21,239 --> 01:08:23,783
when you say
'I had to open my mouth and talk."'

1033
01:08:23,866 --> 01:08:26,661
Like pulling your pants down
and getting the shot

1034
01:08:26,744 --> 01:08:28,621
from the doctor when you're a kid.

1035
01:08:28,705 --> 01:08:31,207
- You gotta mean it.
- I gotta mean this?

1036
01:08:31,291 --> 01:08:35,837
I've done very well
in 31 years of comedy

1037
01:08:35,920 --> 01:08:38,047
without being sincere once.

1038
01:08:38,131 --> 01:08:40,967
Then I ran into this problem.

1039
01:08:41,050 --> 01:08:45,346
- Well, it worked.
- I had to. I was caught.

