1090
01:12:07,090 --> 01:12:11,135
He's a lovely guy. He's the creator
of The Mary Tyler Moore Show

1091
01:12:11,219 --> 01:12:13,805
and As Good As It Gets.

1092
01:12:13,888 --> 01:12:16,933
- Terms of Endearment.
- Very involved in The Simpsons.

1093
01:12:17,016 --> 01:12:19,018
The Simpsons as well.

1094
01:12:19,102 --> 01:12:22,105
He was very curious...

1095
01:12:24,107 --> 01:12:29,862
...about my experience of the
animation process and, you know...

1096
01:12:30,863 --> 01:12:34,742
...how uncomfortable it gets
when you think you can change something

1097
01:12:34,826 --> 01:12:37,704
at a certain stage
and then find out you can't.

1098
01:12:37,787 --> 01:12:40,331
- You experienced that.
- The two...

1099
01:12:40,415 --> 01:12:44,460
He was also a big fan of our TV juniors
that we made for NBC.

1100
01:12:44,544 --> 01:12:47,505
- Really? Has he been watching?
- Yeah.

1101
01:12:47,589 --> 01:12:51,634
He asked me if he could get a DVD
of all of them together.

1102
01:12:51,718 --> 01:12:54,887
- I can get it for him later. Not now.
- Jim Brooks.

1103
01:12:54,971 --> 01:12:57,765
No one ever gets anything
for anybody on the spot.

1104
01:12:57,849 --> 01:13:01,060
- What about Jim Brooks?
